text: Sydonia apomecynoides is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae, and the only species in the genus Sydonia. It was described by Thomson in 1864.Biolib.cz - Sydonia apomecynoides. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphorini Category:Beetles described in 1864
title: Sydonia apomecynoides
